overview: Just in time for your depressingly distanced 2020 Thansgiving, it’s an edition of “Lost & Found Video Night” that’s old enough to vote! “Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 18”!! Featuring psycho public access conspiracy nuts, mind mushing televangelists from around the world, Andy Kaufman ventriloquism, Tarantino pretending to be a tough guy in public, Henry Silva blowing up some guys with a rocket launcher, pre “Pee Wee’s Big Adventure” Pee Wee Herman performing stand up, musical performances from Goblin, The Cardiacs & Gary Wilson as well as some nightmare inducing international musical guests.  Prepare to have your holidays destroyed by the 80+ minute onslaught of what can only be described as “Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 18!”
title: Lost & Found Video Night Vol. 18
